SUMMARY:MAKE Roanoke @ Go Green for Grandin
DESCRIPTION:MAKE Roanoke\nMAKE Roanoke will be participating in the Roanoke Public Library's Go Green for Grandin Event at the Raleigh Court Branch Library on April 11 from 10 AM-1PM.\n\nThe event promises to have live music\, several vendors\, snacks\, and fun! Go Green for Grandin encourages our community to go outside\, take care of our planet\, and invest in sustainable practices. For more information\, please call the library at 540-853-2240.
